summary:
Working with SAP business process design, I derive satisfaction from contributing to efficient, smart and logical working methods.
I work comfortably at the interface of external and internal customers, management and project teams to create buy in and alignment.
Setting up a business in a developing economy has taught me adaptability, creative thinking, to focus on solutions and how to keep your sense of humor.
I have lived and worked in 6 countries on 3 continents, and revel in the creativity and excellence that people from everywhere offer. 

Keywords: change management, business process, order management, order to cash, MS Office, SAP,  Sales and Distribution, Materials Management Purchasing, SOX, Sarbanes Oxley, project management, marketing promotion, customer service trainer, stakeholder management, diving, PADI
